<figureCitation box="[481,616,198,220]" captionStart="Figures 58–59" captionStartId="40.[164,254,778,797]" captionTargetBox="[422,1182,201,745]" captionTargetId="figure-438@40.[419,1188,198,749]" captionTargetPageId="40" captionText="Figures 58–59. Quichuana salvadorensis sp. nov. male holotype genitalia, lateral view: 58, hypandrium; 59, epandrium. Scale bar: 1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5408571" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5408571/files/figure.png" pageId="41" pageNumber="113">Figs 58, 59</figureCitation>
